{
  "title": "Smoky Velvety Norwegian Currant Dumplings",
  "description": "A traditional Norwegian dish featuring smoky, velvety dumplings infused with currants, perfect for a hangover cure. This sugar-free-friendly recipe is a unique twist on a classic comfort food.",
  "cuisine": "Norwegian",
  "diet": [
